---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import settings from '../data/settings.json';
---

<Layout title="Practical Information" description="Everything you need to know about getting to Big Brue - venue, transport, accommodation and accessibility.">
  <section class="bg-blush pt-36 md:pt-40 pb-16 md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-sludge tracking-tight mb-4">
          PRACTICAL INFO
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-sludge/80 leading-relaxed">
          Everything you need to know about visiting Big Brue at Hauser & Wirth Somerset.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Venue -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-sludge mb-4">THE VENUE</h2>
          <p class="text-xl font-medium text-warm-black/80 mb-4">Hauser & Wirth Somerset</p>
          <p class="text-warm-black/70 mb-6">
            Big Brue takes place on the grounds of Hauser & Wirth Somerset. The stunning countryside and world-class art destination provide the perfect backdrop for a weekend of inspiring conversations.
          </p>
          <address class="not-italic text-warm-black/70 mb-6">
            <strong class="text-warm-black">{settings.venue.address}</strong>
          </address>
          <a
            href={settings.venue.mapUrl}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-sludge hover:bg-sludge-dark text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
            </svg>
            View on Google Maps
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/hauser-wirth-somerset.jpg" alt="Hauser & Wirth Somerset" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Getting There -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-stone">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-sludge mb-12 text-center">GETTING THERE</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-bright rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sludge-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 10h18M3 14h18m-9-4v8m-7 0h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-sludge mb-2">By Train</h3>
          <p class="text-warm-black/70 mb-4">
            Bruton station is a 10-minute walk from Hauser & Wirth. Direct trains run from London Paddington (2 hours) via Castle Cary.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-warm-black/60 space-y-1">
            <li>London Paddington - 2 hours</li>
            <li>Bristol Temple Meads - 1 hour</li>
            <li>Bath Spa - 45 minutes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-bright rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sludge-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-sludge mb-2">By Car</h3>
          <p class="text-warm-black/70 mb-4">
            Limited parking only available. We encourage guests to travel by train or public transport where possible. Bruton is just off the A303, easily accessible from London (2.5 hours) and Bristol (1 hour).
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-warm-black/60 space-y-1">
            <li>From A303: Take the Wincanton exit</li>
            <li>Follow signs to Bruton</li>
            <li>Venue signposted from village centre</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Accommodation -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-sludge mb-4 text-center">ACCOMMODATION</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-warm-black/70 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Bruton and the surrounding area offer a range of accommodation options, from boutique hotels to cosy B&Bs and camping.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-blush rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sludge mb-2">At The Chapel</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-sludge/70 mb-3">Boutique hotel in the heart of Bruton</p>
          <span class="text-xs bg-sludge/10 text-sludge px-2 py-1 rounded-full">5 min walk</span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-stone rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sludge mb-2">The Newt</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-sludge/70 mb-3">Luxury estate hotel with gardens</p>
          <span class="text-xs bg-sludge/10 text-sludge px-2 py-1 rounded-full">10 min drive</span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-bright rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sludge-dark mb-2">Bruton Camping</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-sludge-dark/70 mb-3">Festival camping near the venue</p>
          <span class="text-xs bg-sludge-dark/10 text-sludge-dark px-2 py-1 rounded-full">On site</span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-sludge rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Local B&Bs</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mb-3">Various options in and around Bruton</p>
          <span class="text-xs bg-white/10 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Various</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-warm-black/60 mt-8">
        Book early - accommodation in Bruton fills up quickly during events.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Accessibility -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-blush">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-sludge mb-4 text-center">ACCESSIBILITY</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-sludge/70 text-center mb-12">
        We're committed to making Big Brue accessible to everyone.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-sludge mb-4">On Site</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-warm-black/70">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-bright shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Step-free access to all main areas
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-bright shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Accessible toilets throughout
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-bright shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Reserved seating areas for wheelchair users
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-bright shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Assistance dogs welcome
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-sludge mb-4">Support Available</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-warm-black/70">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-bright shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Free tickets for personal assistants
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-bright shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                BSL interpreters at selected events
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-bright shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Quiet room available
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-bright shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Large print programmes
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-stone">
          <p class="text-warm-black/70 text-center">
            Have specific requirements? <a href={`mailto:${settings.contact.email}?subject=Accessibility Enquiry`} class="text-bright font-bold hover:text-bright-dark">Get in touch</a> and we'll do our best to help.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Bring -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-sludge text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-8 text-center">WHAT TO BRING</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-bright mb-3">Essentials</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/80 text-sm">
            <li>Your ticket (digital or printed)</li>
            <li>Valid ID for concessions</li>
            <li>Sun cream & sunglasses</li>
            <li>Layers (British weather!)</li>
            <li>Comfortable walking shoes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-bright mb-3">Recommended</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/80 text-sm">
            <li>Reusable water bottle</li>
            <li>Blanket for outdoor seating</li>
            <li>Camera</li>
            <li>Notebook for inspiration</li>
            <li>Cash (some stalls)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-bright mb-3">Not Permitted</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/80 text-sm">
            <li>Outside alcohol</li>
            <li>Dogs (except assistance)</li>
            <li>Drones</li>
            <li>Professional cameras (without pass)</li>
            <li>Umbrellas in marquees</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-sludge mb-4">QUESTIONS?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-warm-black/70 mb-8">
        Check our FAQ or get in touch with the team.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/faq" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-stone hover:bg-stone/80 text-sludge font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors">
          View FAQs
        </a>
        <a href={`mailto:${settings.contact.email}`} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-sludge hover:bg-sludge-dark text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
